               stealing a pewter quart pot
            </rs>, the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18161204-48-victim405" type="victimName">
                     Samuel 
                     Nice
                  <interp inst="t18161204-48-victim405" type="surname" value="Nice"></interp>
